oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Gene Autry's Melody Ranch - 1948-07-11 - Part 2
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Gene Autry's Melody Ranch, originally broadcast 1948-07-11 (part 2) over the CBS network. Featuring Gene Autry, Pat Buttram, the Cass County Boys, the Pinafores, Carl Cotner, with announcer John "Junior" Jacobs (Johnny Bond is mentioned as being absent). Sponsored by Wrigley's Gum.
